        "subject": "ldlm: Remove use of SLAB_DESTROY_BY_RCU",
        "message": "ldlm: Remove use of SLAB_DESTROY_BY_RCU\n\nThe flag was renamed in later kernels anyway and in RHEL7.[345]\nit seems to be totally broken leading to frequent use after free\nproblems.\n\nWhatever this was tryign to accomplish needs to be done by other means\nif it'sstill a problem I guess.\n\nChange-Id: I3c050ca70c4d421a9f5168cd204b9378c0b9bd71\nSigned-off-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\n"
